Package: eikondata
Type: Package
Title: Eikon Scripting API for R
Version: 1.0.2
Author: MBS
Maintainer: MBS <alejandro.abraham@cerved.com>
Description: Provides a lightweight R interface to the LSEG Eikon Data API,
    enabling programmatic access to real-time and historical market data directly
    from Eikon or via the Eikon API Proxy. The package supports retrieving time series,
    metadata, and price data for financial instruments using simple function calls,
    and returns data in structured R data frames. Requires a valid Refinitiv Eikon
    license and an active Eikon session or proxy.
License: Apache License 2.0
